         <LEFTI>
            <SUITABILITY>
               <P>The tenderer must be a legally established company.</P>
               <P>In order to issue a route permit, the tenderer must comply with necessary requirements in the Professional Transport Act.</P>
               <P>Tenderers must have good competence and experience from equivalent assignments in route areas with more than 50 000 inhabitants.</P>
               <P>Tenderers shall have the ability to carry out procurements and organise the operation/maintenance of electric buses with the accompanying charging infrastructure during the contract period, cf. points 23.6.2 and 23.6.5 in the contract.</P>
