               <P>A pledge from a bank or an insurance company verifying that a licence guarantee statement that covers the always current guarantee sum given by the licence authority for this year, multiplied by the number of buses included in the assignment. The pledge for a licence guarantee shall be calculated from the number of buses in the current contract.</P>
               <P>Confirmation from a bank, insurance or financing institution shall be enclosed stating that a bank guarantee for correct fulfilment of the contract will be provided if the tenderer is awarded the contract.</P>
